create cluster
manual 
------
1. search mongodb atlas
2. login & provide basic info
3. MO, Name - Cluster0, Provider-aws, Region - N.Virginia = create deployment
4. Connect to Cluster0 - taker username & Password
5. create database user
6. Connect to cluster0 -> Connect to your application -> select Driver

# if you access another user
1. select Database Access
2. select password Authentication method
3. Build in Role -> READ & Write to any user
4. click on 'Add User' this button

# Network Acess
 - Allow Acess from anywhere 
 - 0.0.0.0

